00:32:46,977 --> 00:32:49,730
ladies and gentlemen,
our next offering, we hope,

355
00:32:49,855 --> 00:32:52,984
is of a somewhat more playful nature.

356
00:32:53,108 --> 00:32:55,782
- Playful as you wish.
- Thank you.

357
00:32:59,198 --> 00:33:00,165
Oh! No, it isn't!

