00:59:42,174 --> 00:59:44,017
No, no... no.

694
00:59:44,134 --> 00:59:45,761
Lay upon the bed.

695
00:59:51,392 --> 00:59:53,565
Pan your legs.

696
00:59:53,686 --> 00:59:54,983
Crook your knee.

697
00:59:55,104 --> 00:59:56,947
Right arm as thus.

698
00:59:58,148 --> 01:00:01,448
Hand upon the head.
No... as in despair.

699
01:00:39,773 --> 01:00:41,195
Yes.

700
01:00:56,457 --> 01:00:59,757
Eliza... or Liza?

701
01:01:01,045 --> 01:01:02,547
Eliza.

702
01:01:04,006 --> 01:01:05,508
Or Liza.

703
01:01:06,884 --> 01:01:09,979
