725
01:07:59,755 --> 01:08:03,055
No, thank you, madam.
I purchased a potato on the boat.

726
01:08:03,175 --> 01:08:06,054
I should think that were all
you could manage on the steamer.

727
01:08:06,178 --> 01:08:08,101
It was somewhat turbulent.

728
01:08:08,221 --> 01:08:10,690
I shall leave you
to take your refreshment.

729
01:08:10,766 --> 01:08:14,145
Madam, may I apprehend you
with my condolences?

730
01:08:14,853 --> 01:08:16,275
Oh...

731
01:08:16,521 --> 01:08:17,613
I do thank you, sir.

732
01:08:17,731 --> 01:08:21,611
My sympathies, commiserations,
for the loss of your dear departed man.

733
01:08:21,735 --> 01:08:24,079
Well, he were a dear man.

734
01:08:27,115 --> 01:08:31,871
'Tis twice in my life now
I have found myself a widow.

735
01:08:33,246 --> 01:08:36,876
